<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idca021c85-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598" identifier="/us/usc/t43/s620n"><num value="620n">§ 620n.</num><heading> Water quality study and reports</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Secretary of the Interior is directed to continue studies and to make a report to the Congress and to the States of the Colorado River Basin on the quality of water of the Colorado River.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idca021c86-3a70-11f1-bde1-a5140e158598">(<ref href="/us/act/1956-04-11/ch203/s15">Apr. 11, 1956, ch. 203, § 15</ref>, <ref href="/us/stat/70/111">70 Stat. 111</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
